text:
City Missions Church...is a cosy and warm group of passionate  visionary believers with God's heart and business at the centre of it all.It is a place not just for spiritual growth  but mental too , knowledgeable and aware of the endtime news , to prepare believers to be strong and mature in spirit and truth, to help others beyond the four walls of the church.
An all rounded Church group with many experienced leaders ,anointed and equipped in various  specialty ministries from Prayer to Missions , Praise and Intentional Worship ,Inner Healing to Hebraic studies, The Apostolic to Prophetic, the Teaching of the WORD and Disciple making to become Leaders but most of all THE LORD JESUS at the Centre of it all.

A God-centered community that exists to further the Kingdom outreach to the uttermost parts of the earth. The leadership team is extremely committed to the Truth and every part of their many ministries reflects that uncompromising passion.

For my 50th Birthday my son gave surprise gift for Singapore trip and I went to this Church for Christmas,my b'day. What a Blessing. This time I was there on Mother's Day. They honoured all mothers with special Prayer, Songs and Gift. Above all on both occasions Pastor. Joseph Prince gave God's word which was very touching. This much of crowd and young people you can't see in any Church. If you go to Singapore please go to this Church atleast once. God Bless You.
A place to Grow. Spiritually, mentally.
